(2, 8, 'John', 'burmjohn@gmail.com', 'http://fatassblog.com', '69.123.36.43', '2005-10-09 01:42:55', '2005-10-09 00:42:55', '\r\nI hear yea. So are you going to go on the low carb diet again?  I just started my low carb diet and I am going to blog my progress along the way.  I just finished setting up my blog @ http://FatAssBlog.com, swing by and drop a note when you have a chance.\r\n\r\n- John\r\n<a href="http://FatAssBlog.com" rel="nofollow">http://FatAssBlog.com</a>', 0, '1', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows; U; Windows NT 5.1; en-US; rv:1.7.12) Gecko/20050915 Firefox/1.0.7', '', 0, 0),
(3, 8, 'dronkie', 'bellis@i2q.co.uk', 'http://www.mukudu.net', '82.36.154.234', '2005-10-10 22:18:04', '2005-10-10 21:18:04', 'Good luck, worked for me.  I am not sure I will be following as strict a regime, but I will be taking stock of tyh my eating habits in the next week or so.  Just got to clear my head a little.\r\n\r\nBTW, thanks for the comment, you are officially the first one!\r\n\r\nCheers\r\n', 0, '1', 'Mozilla/4.0 (compatible; MSIE 6.0; Windows 98; .NET CLR 1.1.4322)', '', 0, 1);

